{"tid":108254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅馬尼亞政府跪低　撤回縱容貪官法令","createTime":"2017-02-05T06:18:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T06:25:49.000Z","uid":37554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e2204ceff91dbbcb9a4f0d4074ec82fd8d48894","tid":108254,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:18:45.000Z","msg":"羅馬尼亞首都布加勒斯特連續5日爆發反政府示威，抗議政府推出被指縱容貪官的法令。羅馬尼亞總理格林代亞努昨日（2月4日）晚上發聲明，宣布會在今日的內閣特別會議撤回法令，期望化解危機。 格林代亞努在電視發表聲明，指不希望國家撕裂，並會就檢討司法制度展開公眾諮詢。 羅馬尼亞政府上周二繞過國會，以緊急法令方式通過刑法修正案，客許濫權而造成經濟損失不超過約36萬港元，官員便不算干犯刑事罪行。 有關法案引發1989年共產政權倒台以來，最大規模的反政府示威。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://buff.ly/2jNXFej\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbuff.ly%2F2jNXFej&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85Hf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=ea3785a1\" target=\"_blank\">buff.ly/2jNXFej</a>"},{"pid":"88ff1c7a98cc9520fbb50afcc597805f10967b23","tid":108254,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:21:57.000Z","msg":"呢條法律又戇鳩d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc39acaab2fc647cce2f5f054dff28a17e9e94f","tid":108254,"uid":39974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:22:43.000Z","msg":"貪污合法化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351851b0855083429a17c472e519e21b5c5aa5ac","tid":108254,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:25:49.000Z","msg":"屌學下香港啦8700萬都冇問題"}]}